msgid "A large door with a metallic handle."
msgstr "巨大的門，有著金屬門把。"

msgid "Open it?"
msgstr "打開它嗎？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Frozen inside, you see..."
msgstr "冷藏其中，妳看到..."

msgid "...Fingers!"
msgstr "...手指！"

msgid "Wait... arms...? Are these... human arms...?"
msgstr "等等...手臂...？這些是...人的手臂嗎...？"

msgid "Neatly stacked inside the fridge, there's fifty or so arms of different sizes, cut off from their bodies."
msgstr "整齊堆疊在冰箱的是，大約五十隻不同大小的手臂，從它們的身體上被切下來。"

msgid "Both left and right arms can be seen."
msgstr "左右手臂都有。"

msgid "....."
msgstr "....."

msgid "The arms prevent you from closing the door."
msgstr "手臂讓你無法把門關上。"

msgid "It won't open."
msgstr "打不開。"

msgid "Better not to open it."
msgstr "最好不要打開。"
